      "rationale": "Validation experiments performed on the FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry — the same geometry as the COU device. Operating conditions (flow 2–8 L/min, speed 2000–4000 rpm) span the COU envelope. Fluid is porcine blood at physiological hematocrit, matching COU fluid properties within accepted analogue criteria.",
