      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD engineer independent of the analyst. Checklist covering boundary condition assignment, turbulence model selection, hemolysis model constants, and post-processing scripts completed and signed. All discrepancies resolved prior to submission.",
