      "rationale": "RANS k-ω SST turbulence model selected based on published benchmark studies for blood pump flows (Fraser et al. 2011, Hariharan et al. 2011). Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al.) calibrated against independent dataset. Model form uncertainty estimated via comparison against LES results at design point; NIH difference <12%.",
